      bio: "Tobias tries to stay on the cutting edge of Java and Cloud technologies. Holding a Masters Degree in Software Engineering he is responsible for platform engineering and DevOps across all commercial banking platforms at RBC. In his role as Senior Engineering Manager he codes, is involved in architecture, builds DevOps pipelines, experiments with and introduces new technologies to banking projects and mentors RBC developers in best practices. When he is not learning something new he likes to see how far he can run before his legs fall off in an attempt to better his previous marathon time!",
      sourceUrl: "https://2019.cusec.net/speakers",
